#: portal/forms.py:790
msgid ""
"An upload is required for each of the Documents below. These should be "
"prepared on one of the provided templates where available. The limit on "
"space in all sections of the templates should be adhered to and the typeface "
"should be 11 point, Times or similar type font, single spacing (11 point), "
"with margins of 2 cm on the left and 2 cm on the right sides of the page. "
"Instructions in italic may be removed, but not the margins."
msgstr ""
"Me tukuatu ia Tuhinga i raro.  Me whakarite ēnei ki tētahi o ngā tauira kua "
"whakaratoa ina wātea ana. Me ū ki te tepenga mokowā o ngā wāhanga katoa o "
"ngā tauira, ā, me 11 rahinga te atahanga, me Times, he mea ōrite rānei te "
"momo tuhi, kia kotahi te mokowā (11 rahinga), me ngā paenga o te 2 cm i te "
"taha mauī me te 2 cm i te taha matau o te whārangi. Ka taea te tango ngā "
"tohutohu he kuputuhi tītaha te āhua, engari kaua ngā paenga. Hei whakatika i "
"tētahi tuhinga kua tukuna atu, me pāwhiri \"Browse\", ka tonoa koe mō te "
"tauwāhi kōnae hōu; ka pāwhiri \"Tiaki\" hei whakakapi i te kōnae onāianei. "
"Mō ētahi mōhiohio anō tirohia: Whakarāpopototanga me Ngā Puka"

#: portal/forms.py:798
msgid ""
"To revise an uploaded document, click \"Browse\" and you will be prompted "
"for the new file location; and then \"Save\" to replace the existing file."
msgstr ""

