"\n"
"<p>Ko ngā tautuhinga Tauira Whakamaru ka whakamahia e mātau hei whakatau i "
"ngā mea ka taea te tuari mōu mē ngā mea kāore e pai. </p><p>Ko ngā "
"tautuhinga Tauira Whakamaru ka Me mōhio koe i ahu mai ēnei kōwhiringa mai i "
"te Pūnaha Mōhiohio Rangahau o Aotearoa (NZRIS), me pēhea te whakahaere, ā, "
"ka pēhea te whakaatu i ō raraunga ki te NZRIS. </p><p>He aki utauta tō ia "
"kōwhiringa hei whakamārama i ngā mea kei te whakahaerehia. Mēnā e hiahia ana "
"koe kia mōnehu he whakamarutanga, me tuhi mō āhea tango ai i te "
"whakamarutanga. </p>\n"
"  "

