"        "

#: portal/templates/profile_section.html:22
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Career stage is requested to be able to understand the proportion of "
"researchers at different stages of their career.\n"
"        The expectation is that this will assist in the development of "
"funding mechanisms and support tools.\n"
"        Only used at aggregated levels for statistical and reporting "
"purposes.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        E tonoa ana he raupapa ara mahi kia mārama ai ki te ōwehenga o ngā "
"kairangahau i te wāhanga rerekē o tōna ara mahi rerekē.\n"
"Ko te manako ka āwhina tēnei ki te hanga tikanga tuku pūtea me ngā utauta "
"tautoko.\n"
"Ka whakamahia anake i ngā taumata tōpū mō ngā kaupapa tatauranga me te tuku "
"pūrongo.\n"
"        "

#: portal/templates/profile_section.html:28
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Identifiers that are yours in public systems, e.g. authenticated "
"ORCID iD, Scopus ID, ResearcherID, and Teacher Registration Number.\n"
"        Please DO NOT enter personal identifiers such as IRD Number, "
"National Student Number or National Health Number.\n"
"      "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Ko ō pūtautuhi i roto i ngā pūnaha tūmatanui, hei tauira, ORCID ID "
"kua whakatūturutia, ID Kairangahau, me te Tau Rēhita Kaiako. KAUA e tāuru "
"pūtautuhi whaiaro pērā i te Tau IRD, Tau Ākonga ā-Motu, Tau Hauora ā-Motu "
"rānei.\n"
"        "

#: portal/templates/profile_section.html:34
msgid ""
"\n"
"          For NZ-based researchers, a current CV in the\n"
"          <a href=\"https://www.royalsociety.org.nz/assets/documents/NZ-RST-"
"CV-Template.doc\">NZ RST CV Template</a> is requested.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Mō ngā kairangahau kei Aotearoa, e tonoa ana he tāhuhu tangata onāianei i "
"roto i te           <a href=\"https://www.royalsociety.org.nz/assets/"
"documents/NZ-RST-CV-Template.doc\">Tauira Tāhuhu Tangata NZ RST CV</a>.\n"
"        "

#: portal/templates/profile_section.html:39
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "\n"
#| "        Curriculum Vitae are required from the following:\n"
